The paper discusses the use of computational methods for analyzing medical images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of point distribution models and deep learning-based approaches, which are commonly used in medical imaging and fall under the modeling and simulation (cs.MS) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
